OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police marksman may
OL,7,Fhave been "angry, frustrated and
OL,8,Fannoyed" when he took the decision to
OL,9,Fshoot to kill Chris Kaba, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FMartyn Blake, 40, has gone on trial at
OL,13,Fthe Old Bailey charged with murdering
OL,14,FMr Kaba.
OL,16,FThe 24-year-old was in the driving
OL,17,Fseat of an Audi car when he was shot
OL,18,Fin the head in Streatham, south
OL,19,FLondon, on September 6 2022.
