OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,FProsecutor Tom Little KC told jurors
OL,7,FBlake's decision to use lethal force
OL,8,Fwas "not reasonably justified or
OL,9,Fjustifiable".
OL,11,FHe told jurors: "The defendant did not
OL,12,Fknow the man he shot. What he was
OL,13,Fthinking at the time only he knows.
OL,15,F"But you may want to consider in this
OL,16,Fcase whether the requests that were
OL,17,Fmade to Chris Kaba by the police that
OL,18,Fhe did not obey caused the defendant
OL,19,Fto become angry, frustrated and
OL,20,Fannoyed."
