OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,FOpening the case on Wednesday, Mr
OL,7,FLittle said: "This case involves a
OL,8,Fdecision by this defendant to shoot
OL,9,FChris Kaba with the intention to kill.
OL,10,FIt was a decision taken to use lethal
OL,11,Fforce with a firearm by a firearms
OL,12,Fofficer in the Metropolitan Police.
OL,14,F"It was a decision to shoot which was
OL,15,Ftaken when, we say, the unassailable
OL,16,Fevidence of what actually took place
OL,17,Fthat night reveals that it was not
OL,18,Freasonably justified or justifiable."
