OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,FIt should be a "remedy of last resort"
OL,7,Ffor a firearms officer to shoot and
OL,8,Fkill, jurors were told.
OL,10,FBut the prosecutor said: "The body-
OL,11,Fworn footage and footage from cameras
OL,12,Fon police vehicles reveals, we say,
OL,13,Fthat it was not necessary to shoot.
OL,15,F"The immediate risk to both the
OL,16,Fdefendant and his fellow officers at
OL,17,Fthe scene did not, we say, justify at
OL,18,Fthe point when the trigger was pulled,
OL,19,Ffiring a bullet into the vehicle that
OL,20,FChris Kaba was driving .
