OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,F"That is why, we say, that this is a
OL,7,Fcase of murder rather than the use of
OL,8,Flawful self-defence or lawful defence
OL,9,Fof another by the defendant."
OL,11,FAt the point Blake shot Mr Kaba in the
OL,12,Fhead, the vehicle he was in was
OL,13,Fstationary, jurors heard.
OL,15,FThe young man had just reversed a
OL,16,Fshort distance backwards, striking the
OL,17,Ffront of a police vehicle that was
OL,18,Fblocking it in, having previously
OL,19,Fattempted to drive forwards, jurors
OL,20,Fheard.
