OL,3,CAnger may have played part in decision
OL,4,Cto shoot to kill Chris Kaba, court told
OL,6,FMr Little said: "We say that on
OL,7,Fcareful analysis nothing Chris Kaba
OL,8,Fdid in the second before he was shot
OL,9,Fjustified this defendant's decision to
OL,10,Fshoot."
OL,12,FMembers of Mr Kaba's family, including
OL,13,Fhis parents, sat in the well of the
OL,14,Fcourt just metres from Blake in the
OL,15,Fdock, as Mr Little laid out the case
OL,16,Ffor the prosecution.
OL,18,FBlake has denied murder and the trial
OL,19,Fbefore Mr Justice Goss continues.
